#### Automated Verification

- [ ] `pnpm --filter @repo/app-trpc typecheck` passes
- [ ] `pnpm --filter @repo/app-trpc build` (if one exists) passes
- [ ] `apps/app` still typechecks (`pnpm --filter app typecheck`) — async `getAuthHeaders` change is backwards-compatible.

#### Manual Verification

- [ ] `apps/app` in browser still loads and hydrates tRPC queries (regression).
- [ ] `import { DesktopTRPCProvider } from "@repo/app-trpc/desktop"` resolves in a scratch TS file.

